headline: Jabil Announces Date for Fourth Quarter and Fiscal Year 2025 Earnings Release and 8th Annual Investor Briefing
summary: ST. PETERSBURG, Fla., September 11, 2025--Jabil Inc. (NYSE: JBL) today announced it will release its fourth quarter and fiscal year 2025 financials on Thursday, September 25, 2025, before the market opens.

headline: Aeva Technologies’ (AEVA) Multibagger Momentum Fueled by LiDAR Innovation in $80 Billion Market
summary: Aeva Technologies Inc. (NASDAQ:AEVA) is one of the best multibagger stocks to invest in right now. The company develops next-generation 4D-LiDAR sensors for autonomous driving and industrial applications.
